

<div class="component">
	<header>Select Menu</header>

	<section>
		<h3>BC-Select</h3>
		<p>
			select menu.
		</p>
		Properties:
		<ul>
			<li>model - array of objects with key:value pair. required.</li>
			<li>itemLabel - the key or value to use as the item label. required.</li>
			<li>onSelect - the action to run when an object is selected. the selected object can be passed to action.</li>
		</ul>
		Code:
		<code>\{{bc-select model=model onSelect="runAction" itemLabel='label'}}</code>
		Result:
		<span class="code-result">
			{{bc-select class="left" model=model.select itemLabel='label'}}
		</span>
	</section>
</div>


<div class="component">
	<header>Inputs</header>

	<section>
		<h3>BC-Checkbox</h3>
		<p>
			checkbox input.
		</p>
		Properties:
		<ul>
			<li>title - label to display next to checkbox.</li>
			<li>value - the boolean value to toggle with the checkbox.</li>
		</ul>
		Code:
		<code>
			\{{bc-checkbox title="check me" value=isChecked}} <br />
			\{{if isChecked 'checked!' 'not checked!'}}
		</code>
		Result:
		<span class="code-result">
			{{bc-checkbox title="check me" value=isChecked}}
			{{if isChecked 'checked!' 'not checked!'}}
		</span>
		<h3>BC-Radio-Button</h3>
		<p>
			radio button input.
		</p>
		Properties:
		<ul>
			<li>label - label to display next to radio button.</li>
			<li>name - the name of the group that the radio button belongs to.</li>
			<li>value - the value of the radio button. must be unique from all others with same name.</li>
			<li>onSelect - action to run when button selected.</li>
		</ul>
		Code:
		<code>
			\{{bc-radio-button value="option1" label="option 1" onSelect="runAction" name="options"}}<br/>
			\{{bc-radio-button value="option2" label="option 2" onSelect="runAction" name="options"}}
		</code>
		Result:
		<span class="code-result">
			{{bc-radio-button value="option1" label="option 1" onSelect="runAction" name="options"}}<br/>
			{{bc-radio-button value="option2" label="option 2" onSelect="runAction" name="options"}}
			<p>{{result}}</p>
		</span>
		<h3>BC-Validate</h3>

		<p>textfield with built-in validation error display.</p>
		Properties:
		<ul>
			<li>label - label to display above text field.</li>
			<li>value - the value to set with the input.</li>
			<li>placeholder - text to display if no value is present. defaults to label.</li>
			<li>required - set whether or not the field is required. boolean. defauls to false.</li>
			<li>requiredError - error message to show when input is required and not set. Defaults to <em>This is a required field</em>.</li>
			<li>validateExpression - regular expression to validate input against.</li>
			<li>invalidError - error message to show when input is invalid. Defaults to <em>The input is invalid</em>.</li>
			<li>showLabel - set whether or not to display the label. boolean. defaults to true.</li>
			<li>maxlength - maximum allowed character input.</li>
		</ul>
		Code:
		<code>
			\{{bc-validate label="Coupon Code" value=coupon required=true requiredError="you must fill out this field." maxlength="256"}} <br />
		</code>
		Result:
		<span class="code-result">
			{{bc-validate label="Coupon Code" value=coupon required=true requiredError="you must fill out this field." maxlength="256"}}
		</span>
	</section>
</div>

<div class="component">
	<header>
		BC-List
	</header>
	<section>
		<p>list view of an array of objects.</p>
		Properties:
		<ul>
			<li>selector - set whether or not the rows are selectable. boolean. defaults to false.</li>
			<li>headerItems - array of strings to set as column headers.</li>
		</ul>
		Code:
		<code>
			\{{#bc-list headerItems=headerItems hasImage=true selector=true onClick="runClickAction" model=model.people as |item|}}<br />
				<span class="indent">&lt;span&gt;\{{item.name}}&lt;/span&gt;<br />
				&lt;span&gt;\{{item.occupation}}&lt;/span&gt;<br />
				&lt;span&gt;\{{item.age}}&lt;/span&gt;</span><br />
			\{{/bc-list}}
		</code>
		Result:
		<span class="code-result">
			{{#bc-list headerItems=headerItems hasImage=true selector=true onClick="runClickAction" model=model.people as |item|}}
				<span>{{item.name}}</span>
				<span>{{item.occupation}}</span>
				<span>{{item.age}}</span>
			{{/bc-list}}
		</span>
	</section>
</div>


